title: Walker Hayes on What it’s Like To Be Famous and His Favorite Song on His New Album + Bobby’s Top 3 Favorite Sugary Things + Lunchbox Records an Uncomfortable Situation with Neighbor
itunes:title: Walker Hayes on What it’s Like To Be Famous and His Favorite Song on His New Album + Bobby’s Top 3 Favorite Sugary Things + Lunchbox Records an Uncomfortable Situation with Neighbor
description:
Walker Hayes stops by the studio to talk about his new album, what it’s like to be famous vs. non-famous, and the secret to his abs. Bobby shares a story on how people believe that eating healthy during the day gives you permission to eat unhealthy food at night. Lunchbox recorded his neighbor complaining to him about his Christmas lights still being up.
